# Component & Styling Patterns

## File Structure

Each section component lives in `src/components/sections/` with a colocated CSS module:
```
SectionName.tsx
SectionName.module.css
```

Reusable UI primitives live in `src/components/ui/`.
Layout components (Header, Footer) live in `src/components/layout/`.

## Section Component Template

```tsx
import styles from "./SectionName.module.css";
import { SectionTag } from "@/components/ui/SectionTag";

interface SectionNameProps {
  // typed props
}

export function SectionName({ ...props }: SectionNameProps) {
  return (
    <section className={styles.section}>
      <div className={styles.inner}>
        <SectionTag text="SECTION LABEL" />
        {/* content */}
      </div>
    </section>
  );
}
```

## CSS Module Pattern

```css
.section {
  width: 100%;
  padding: var(--section-padding) 0;
  /* use token for background: var(--bg-dark), var(--color-smoke), etc. */
}

.inner {
  max-width: var(--content-width);
  margin: 0 auto;
  padding-inline: var(--page-padding);
}
```

## Full-Bleed Right Pattern

For content (like blog cards) that extends past the right content boundary:

```css
.section {
  overflow: hidden;
}

.inner {
  padding-left: max(var(--page-padding), calc((100vw - var(--content-width)) / 2 + var(--page-padding)));
  padding-right: 0;
}
```

## Carousel Pattern

Horizontal scroll carousel (e.g. blog listing):

```css
.track {
  display: flex;
  gap: 32px;
  overflow-x: auto;
  scrollbar-width: none;
  -ms-overflow-style: none;
}

.track::-webkit-scrollbar {
  display: none;
}
```

Navigation via `ArrowNav` component, scrolling via `scrollBy({ left: cardWidth + gap, behavior: "smooth" })`.

## Responsive Breakpoints

Three breakpoints, desktop first:

- Default: full layout
- `@media (max-width: 1024px)`: tablet — stack columns, reduce padding
- `@media (max-width: 767px)`: mobile — single column, minimal padding

## Rules

- Always use CSS modules (`.module.css`), never inline styles for layout
- Use `var(--font-primary)` not `"Manrope"` — same for all fonts and colors
- Every section must have `width: 100%` on its root element
- Use `"use client"` directive only when the component uses hooks, event handlers, or browser APIs
- Prefer `<Image>` from `next/image` for raster images; use native `<img>` only for SVGs that need to fill their container
- All tag text must be ALL CAPS when passed to `SectionTag`
- Import shared UI from `@/components/ui` — check barrel export at `src/components/ui/index.ts`
- Footer uses `border-bottom` on parent containers as row dividers, not separate `<div>` elements
